DomFS - Document Object Model Filesystem
========================================

DomFS is a FUSE implementation that exposes the DOM of a participating
web page as a filesystem.

The DomFS client driver (DomFS.js) can be included in any HTML5 page,
allowing the page to browsed like a regular filesystem.

The code
========

DomFServer.py - Implements a WebSocket server
DomFS.py      - Implements the FUSE bindings
DomFS.js 	  - Implements the filesystem operations on its host DOM.

Tests
=====

test-tree.py  - Nicely prints a DomFS directory tree.
test-style.py - Recursively applies arbitrary CSS styling to tags of a given type.
test-spell.py - Recursively spell-corrects the contents of tags of a given type.
